<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.NutjobLaboratories.Merk</id>
  <name>MERK</name>
  <summary>Multiple-document IRC client built with PyQt</summary>
  <developer_name>Nutjob Laboratories</developer_name>
  <update_contact>nutjob-laboratories@users.noreply.github.com</update_contact>
  <description>
    <p>MERK is a lightweight IRC client written in Python and PyQt. It focuses on a clean interface,
    responsive behavior, and the essentials for everyday IRC chatting without unnecessary bloat.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Connect to multiple servers and channels simultaneously</li>
      <li>Scriptable command system compatible with traditional IRC workflows</li>
      <li>Spellchecking, themes, and extensive UI customization options</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
